<2ND_LINE>AM-Indian Convention,0412</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Indian Congress Sets National Agenda At Annual Convention</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Retransmits a0578 to restore slugline.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By MELISSA JORDAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SIOUX FALLS, S.D. (AP) </DATELINE>
