<HEAD>Rep. Pepper Hospitalized</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: UPDATES throughout with Pepper having growth removed.</NOTE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Rep. Claude Pepper, D-Fla., said Saturday he
